{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"07743391-85a4-4299-9606-db595f47f266","content":"Here's what to change in your `.csproj`:\n\n**1. Remove these packages:**\n- `NUnit3TestAdapter`\n- `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk`\n\n**2. Add this package:**\n- `NUnit.Runner` (4.x+ — this is the Microsoft.Testing.Platform adapter for NUnit)\n\n**3. Update project properties:**\n```xml\n<PropertyGroup>\n  <OutputType>Exe</OutputType>\n  <TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>\n</PropertyGroup>\n```\n\n- `OutputType` is needed because the test project becomes a self-contained executable.\n- `TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport` enables `dotnet test` to work with the new platform.\n\n**4. Run tests as before:**\n```bash\ndotnet test\n```\n\nNo changes to your test code are required — your `[Test]`, `[TestCase]`, `[SetUp]`, etc. attributes all work the same.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"70f368d7-13ca-4061-a04f-244d40237eb3","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user is asking about migrating their NUnit test project from VSTest to Microsoft.Testing.Platform. This is a knowledge question about .NET testing infrastructure migration. Let me provide a concise answer based on my knowledge.\n\nKey changes needed to migrate NUnit from VSTest (NUnit3TestAdapter) to Microsoft.Testing.Platform:\n\n1. Replace `NUnit3TestAdapter` with `NUnit.Runner` (or the appropriate Microsoft.Testing.Platform adapter for NUnit)\n2. Actually, for NUnit with Microsoft.Testing.Platform, you need to use `NUnit.Runner` package which provides the Microsoft.Testing.Platform integration.\n\n\n3. Remove the old `NUnit3TestAdapter` and `Microsoft.NET.Test.Sdk` packages, then add `NUnit.Runner` which handles the Microsoft.Testing.Platform integration\n4. Optionally configure the project file with `<TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>true</TestingPlatformDotnetTestSupport>` to use `dotnet test` with the new platform\n5. Change `<OutputType>Exe</OutputType>` since the test project becomes a self-contained executable rather than a library","outputTokens":740,"requestId":"7C30:1EDE:22296B:288C3E:69F93E1C"},"id":"e7f1b04f-2915-4380-987d-1f9b32f70625","timestamp":"2026-05-05T00:47:38.244Z","parentId":"dd5c80a6-d14d-42d3-a77f-ff537535d4d3"}
